targets.rawSql:
select tab_all.vis_name host_name,
  trim(substring_index(substring_index(tab_all.key_,'[',-1),']',1)) as node,
  sum(case trim(substring_index(substring_index(tab_all.key_,'powerstore.hardware.drives.',-1),'.[',1)) when 'size' then tab_all.value end) as 'Drives Size',
  sum(case trim(substring_index(substring_index(tab_all.key_,'powerstore.hardware.drives.',-1),'.[',1)) when 'status' then tab_all.value end) as 'Drives Status'
from
  (select tab1.vis_name,
    tab1.host_name,
    tab1.itemid,
    tab1.item_name,
    tab1.value,
    tab1.key_
   from (SELECT h.hostid
           ,h.name   vis_name
           ,h.host   host_name
           ,i.itemid
           ,i.name   item_name
           ,i.key_
           ,hs.clock
           ,hs.value
         FROM items i,hosts h,history hs,hosts_groups hg,hstgrp hstg
         where h.hostid = i.hostid and i.itemid = hs.itemid and h.hostid = hg.hostid and hg.groupid = hstg.groupid
           and hstg.name in ($Group)
           and i.key_ like 'powerstore.hardware.drives.%'
           and hs.clock > UNIX_TIMESTAMP(DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 60 minute))) tab1
   where tab1.clock=
    (select max(clock)
     from (SELECT h.hostid
             ,h.name   vis_name
             ,h.host   host_name
             ,i.itemid
             ,i.name   item_name
             ,i.key_
             ,hs.clock
             ,hs.value
           FROM items i,hosts h,history hs,hosts_groups hg,hstgrp hstg
           where h.hostid = i.hostid and i.itemid = hs.itemid and h.hostid = hg.hostid and hg.groupid = hstg.groupid
             and hstg.name in ($Group)
             and i.key_ like 'powerstore.hardware.drives.%'
             and hs.clock > UNIX_TIMESTAMP(DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 60 minute))) tab2
   where tab2.itemid = tab1.itemid)
   union
   select tab1.vis_name,
    tab1.host_name,
    tab1.itemid,
    tab1.item_name,
    tab1.value,
    tab1.key_
   from (SELECT h.hostid
           ,h.name   vis_name
           ,h.host   host_name
           ,i.itemid
           ,i.name   item_name
           ,i.key_
           ,hs.clock
           ,hs.value
         FROM items i,hosts h,history hs,hosts_groups hg,hstgrp hstg
         where h.hostid = i.hostid and i.itemid = hs.itemid and h.hostid = hg.hostid and hg.groupid = hstg.groupid
           and hstg.name in ($Group)
           and i.key_ like 'powerstore.hardware.drives.%'
           and hs.clock > UNIX_TIMESTAMP(DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 60 minute))) tab1
   where tab1.clock=
    (select max(clock)
     from (SELECT h.hostid
             ,h.name   vis_name
             ,h.host   host_name
             ,i.itemid
             ,i.name   item_name
             ,i.key_
             ,hs.clock
             ,hs.value
           FROM items i,hosts h,history hs,hosts_groups hg,hstgrp hstg
           where h.hostid = i.hostid and i.itemid = hs.itemid and h.hostid = hg.hostid and hg.groupid = hstg.groupid
             and hstg.name in ($Group)
             and i.key_ like 'powerstore.hardware.drives.%'
             and hs.clock > UNIX_TIMESTAMP(DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 60 minute))) tab2
where tab2.itemid = tab1.itemid)) tab_all where tab_all.vis_name = '$Hosts' group by node

         where h.hostid = i.hostid and i.itemid = hs.itemid and h.hostid = hg.hostid and hg.groupid = hstg.groupid
           and hstg.name in ($Group)
           and i.key_ like 'powerstore.volume.%'

    (select max(clock)
     from (SELECT h.hostid
             ,h.name   vis_name
             ,h.host   host_name
             ,i.itemid
             ,i.name   item_name
             ,i.key_
             ,hs.clock
             ,hs.value
           FROM items i,hosts h,history_uint hs,hosts_groups hg,hstgrp hstg
           where h.hostid = i.hostid and i.itemid = hs.itemid and h.hostid = hg.hostid and hg.groupid = hstg.groupid
             and hstg.name in ($Group)

where tab2.itemid = tab1.itemid)) tab_all where tab_all.vis_name = '$Hosts' group by node
